Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:57.59,Location Names 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,500)\pos(322,439)}South Central Flonyard, Plains of Cocona
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:11.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Godwin, is the march going smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:14.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your Highness Leonmitchelli.{or Lady.. but she's a Princess, but not addressed as Princess here}{used "your Highness" instead of "your Excellency"}{And "her Highness" was used anyway later on in the script, so wasn't that good? =P}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:16.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain is unfortunate,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:22.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but the entire army will definitely be\N able to reach the fortress by tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.05,0:02:24.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as your Highness has ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to prepare for tomorrow's fortress siege,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:30.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the soldiers have had sufficient rest and food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:43.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, we'll let the Dog Princess of Biscotti experience the humiliation of defeat once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:49.10,Location Names,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,00)\pos(322,439)}Biscotti Republic, City of Frianno
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:59.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure enough, the soldiers of the\N Galette Lion Army are approaching Myon Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:05.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those people from Galette really serious \Nabout fighting their way all the way to this castle?{Those people from Galette are really serious about attacking all the way to this castle?}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:11.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the leader of the Galette Lion Army, \Nher Highness Leonmitchelli, is very brave,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:14.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she's also the type who tends to cross the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:19.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Reasoning aside, we've been losing battle after battle lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:24.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If only Lady d'Arquien{Dalkian} and Madam Tenko were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:29.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Knights Brioche and Yukikaze would share their point of view...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:32.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, if we lose this battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:36.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if the worst happens, our Frianno{does not sound like Frianno or whatever that word is here... aren't they worried about Myon Castle anyway?} Castle would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:38.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:42.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For our princess, and for the people of Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:43.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we have to win this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:45.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:47.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're currently in the presence of the princess, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:51.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse my rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:53.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:57.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've clearly understood the poor situation facing our Biscotti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We most definitely cannot be defeated in this battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:06.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I have decided to use my trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:09.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Trump card?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:12.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a representative of the Biscotti Republic,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:15.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by the name of Millhiore F. Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall summon a Hero to our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:28.03,Location Names 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,00)\pos(322,439)}Japan, City of Kinokawa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:33.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink!{Going to use Sink instead of Shinku?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:35.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink! Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:38.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:43.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then come down already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:46.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're late. I'll leave without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:48.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up! I'll be down in a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:01.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Becky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:03.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:22.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, that was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:29.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, tomorrow is the beginning of our spring break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you planning to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:37.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad and mom will be away on a business trip as usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:40.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was wondering if I should pay a visit to my hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:42.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hometown?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:43.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean back in England?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:46.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, a visit to Cornwall.{It's not the literal translation, but this makes it so much less awkward.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:49.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, there are a lot of places to practice there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:53.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really love athletic things, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:00.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! They're fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:05.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be a big competition in July and September this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't slack on practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:09.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Iron Athletes Championship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:13.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The preliminary qualifying round\N is in July, and the official one is in September.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:17.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was such a waste last year. \NYou were so close to becoming the champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:19.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you came to cheer me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:25.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think getting second is already amazing enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:28.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I somehow still feel like winning this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:31.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll practice like hell this spring break!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:42.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:43.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,During the last three days of spring break,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:49.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will you and your parents be free?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:51.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My parents will be back by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:57.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to visit my villa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Nanami said she'd come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:02.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:05.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, it's just in time for the flower viewing season.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:08.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If your parents are too busy, you can come on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really? On second thought, no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:13.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd just leave me alone like usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:17.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then do athletic or cudgel practice all day{\fscx230}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:22.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll train like hell the day before until I can't stand properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:26.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't overdo it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:31.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later, Becky! \NMake sure you confirm our arrangement!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll e-mail you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:42.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have all of you enjoyed life on campus this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:46.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though all of you were born in different countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:49.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the days you have spent in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:52.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the memories you have with\N your classmates, are all precious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:56.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So from tomorrow's spring break onward...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi, what's going on? Are you leaving early?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:02.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I need to hurry to the airport!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:06.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:23.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Japan is a really great country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:26.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially this city of Kinokawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.29,0:08:28.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's peaceful and convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:33.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there aren't many places to move around and have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:35.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little small
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:50.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If only there was a corpse somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of place where we can make a big fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:28.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:39.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:43.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, ears? A tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:49.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. You must be the Hero who responded to my summoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.76,0:10:55.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the one who summoned you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:11:01.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the leader of the Biscotti Republic, City of Frianno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:04.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Millhiore F. Biscotti.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:07.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Sink Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:10.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are Sir Sink, the Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:12.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I shall address you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:18.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumaki, thanks for escorting{ushering} our Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:19.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:26.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have responded to our summoning and thus have arrived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:30.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am very grateful that you came all the way to Frianno.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:34.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me out about our current situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:38.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then give us the help that we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:42.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, for now, it would be helpful\N if you told me what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:44.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! It has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:51.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What has begun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:57.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our country, Biscotti, is at war with our neighboring country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:17.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it looks like our advance is going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:19.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If these conditions persist, we'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:35.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It has opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:38.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Start advancing from the fortress gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.06,0:12:41.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the day we bring down Frianno Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:46.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make the Dog Princess{one of the early lines of the script was "Dog Princess"; repeated for consistency} and her knights cry out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:12:59.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:02.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your first time seeing a Cerkle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:04.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any where I come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:09.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Cerkle, Haran.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:11.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please mount as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:22.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they are our neighbor,\N Galette often goes to war with our country, Biscotti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:25.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But as of late our country has been continuously losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:28.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They have broken through many \Nof our strongholds and battlefronts,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:32.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and today they're trying to bring down our castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:36.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now we lack the kind of knight who can confront their leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:41.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Galette Lion Army, the King of Beasts, Leonmitchelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:45.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I need you, a Hero, to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:49.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not a knight or a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:51.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a normal middle school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can be of any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, you're too humble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:14:00.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very certain of your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:16.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, the exciting battle continues today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:20.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This live broadcast is brought to you by me, from the country of the Galette Lion Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:21.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Franboise Charley!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:24.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The commentary will be by General Bernard and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.54,0:14:25.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:30.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...Princess Leonmitchelli's personal attendant, Miss Biore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:31.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:36.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With that said, every soldier from the\N Galette Lion Army is finally starting to march!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:40.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The single plank bridge was easily \Nbroken through within twenty minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:42.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up for the soldiers of the Galette Lion Army is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:45.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the Biscotti Republic's pride and joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:48.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Frianno's blockade.{What the -heck- are they shooting?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:59.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the experienced soldiers of \Nthe Lion Army are having a tough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:03.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If they also break through this place, that's it for Biscotti.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:09.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:16.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The rescue work by Biscotti is efficient as usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:17.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,right, Miss Biore?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:21.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they won't give up and continue to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:26.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The commander, her Highness Leonmitchelli, has yet to enter the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:31.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if a promising knight from Biscotti's side \Ncomes out, she'll enter the battle and finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:33.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:40.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Second battalion, advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks pretty bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the Martinozzi siblings?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:56.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Galette Army continues to advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:59.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On the battlefield, a proud young knight from Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:03.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair Martinozzi, has begun to greet the incoming advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! A few got past her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:28.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:29.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there still too many soldiers for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:29.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:09.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was a really close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:14.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The last six people who arrive at the battlefield will be awarded with bonus points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:18.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We really hope to award a special prize to the very last person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:21.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what he said! Soldiers at the front line,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:22.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he said there's a bonus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:24.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:31.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This... is war?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:35.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, is this your first time seeing a battlefield?{there has to be another word for "seeing" hee}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:39.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, will anybody get hurt, or even die, in this war?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:40.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:42.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:45.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire battlefield is bound by the rules of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is fought fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:52.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the responsibility of the organizer to ensure there are no injuries or accidents during the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:57.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, this is also the way \Ncountries negotiate with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:18:00.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though sometimes it'll be more intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:08.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, for Frianno, wars allow citizens to enjoy sports and competition in a healthy way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:12.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost continuously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:17.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The citizens of Biscotti and our knights feel depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:21.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And most importantly, if the palace gets attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone who has been working hard will be disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:26.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:28.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappointed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With war in a alternate world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:35.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the summoning of a Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:39.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this is exactly like the worlds\N in the fantasy novels that Becky likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:44.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I calmly think about this, I'm definitely dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:47.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:48.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:51.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Hero of this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:54.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you were found by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:57.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no doubt that you are the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:59.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the Hero of my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:04.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll acknowledge your summoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:06.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prevent everyone from being disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:09.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Sink the Hero, will give it my all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:13.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:16.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's return to the palace at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:19.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your equipment and weapons have already been prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumaki! Haran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:26.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Haran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Sir Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:38.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:53.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! It's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:56.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haran is really good at flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:06.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if this is a dream or reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:08.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is amazingly interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:11.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a waste if I don't have some fun before I go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:15.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The Princess is coming back with a Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:20.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, we've just received important news!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:24.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Millhiore has summoned a Hero at this critical moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:29.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also my first time seeing a Hero present on the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:34.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of hero will the Hero of Biscotti be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.61,0:20:36.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maidservants of Frianno Castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:40.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,have the Hero's clothes and armor been prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:44.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good. As soon as the Hero arrives,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:46.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,complete his change of clothes within thirty seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:50.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:52.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:53.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:55.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rita, I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:57.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:21:00.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero is here too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:04.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's our wonderful Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:08.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People of Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:10.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and people of the Galette Lion Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:11.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,sorry to keep all of you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:15.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Biscotti has been continuously losing lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:19.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that kind of poor development will end today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:23.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who will bring hope and victory to Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:26.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,our wonderful Hero, has finally arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:41.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He has appeared on the battlefield looking magnificent and striking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:00.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have answered the call of the Princess's summoning!{... there's an 's. no s in 's is a special plural case or the case for some proper nouns. princess isn't a proper noun.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:01.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Sink the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:03.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now face the lot of you!
