Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:53.69,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, Sir Hero, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.69,0:23:55.21,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}L-Landing failed.
